DDEESSCCRRIIPPTTIIOONN
       eeccaassoouunnddrrcc  is  the  main configuration file for ecasound.
       If it doesn't exist, ecasound creates it with default val-
       ues. If it exists, all name-value pairs are read. When you
       quit ecasound, eeccaassoouunnddrrcc is rewritten if resource  values
       have been modified.

       The format is quite simple. One line consists of a config-
       uration variable and its value.  Variable  and  value  are
       separated  with  either '=' or ' '. Lines beginning with a
       "#" are ignored (comment lines).


